{%- comment -%}
  Shown under the card price on the Health Care Professionals collection (healthcare_provider),
  or when card-product is rendered with show_hcp_unit_pricing_note (e.g. customer-tag collection section).
  Pass show_note: true from card-product.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if show_note -%}
  <div class="card__hcp-price-note">
    <p class="card__hcp-price-note__line card__hcp-price-note__line--emphasis">
      Pricing shown per unit.
    </p>
    <p class="card__hcp-price-note__line">
      Orders ship in cases of 12 one-month packs.
    </p>
  </div>
{%- endif -%}
